I've lost a lot of focus for this game; all I have is the original now barely pulsating scum read on Bacde, and DV and Matias as town. Going to have to reread.<br>
<br>
@Elyse - What is your read on me and DV?

@GC: I never believed the hider claim and I've always thought CDB was scum since then. I simply cant vote him or lynch him until we get night action info.<br>
<br>
Especially now. A hider and a jailkeeper is a bit much for a mini normal.

@Equinox would you be willing to vote for FT or GC?<br>
<br>
EPM is a compromise lynch imo

As much as I want to say that Bacde's reaction to the hider business is probably from scum, it appears that at least one other person doesn't know what to make of all the claims, so eh.  Setup spec isn't everyones thing I guess.<br>
<br>
@Equinox: Actually I want to think on that too.  Im like 99% sure that one of them is lying, because frankly all that power in a game is BS and would never pass normal reviews.  My issue with JS's claim is that Cop/JK/Hider is VERY strong and there is not too much mafia power than can counter that effectively.  At least with Doc/Cop/JK, there could easily be a mafia RB/RC that would put a lid on the town power somewhat.
